short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Collapse the menu in the OpenAI ChatGPT interface, that's it!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension adds a button to the top of the OpenAI chatGPT chat menu that allows you to collapse the menu in the OpenAI ChatGPT interface, that's it!

If you like this extension, consider buying me a beer at https://www.buymeacoffee.com/wbrozovic
